casebody.data:
DECKERS OUTDOOR CORPORATION, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-803. Supreme Court of the United States May 19, 2014.

Motion of American Association of Exporters and Importers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae out of time is denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Federal Circuit denied.
